    "In this way, the user's different activities appearing in a time window are observed.",
    "the different weights based on the average of constituent days are assigned for each window.",
    "With the help of these techniques, each user's activity with attention to the category of the time window is marked by proportional weight.",
    "Hence, the smaller weights can be considered for distant time windows.",
    "On the contrary, due to the crucial role of near-time windows, the bigger weights are selected for them."
  ],
